OL,3,CJames Van Der Beek's daughter, 9,
OL,4,Cposts tribute to late father on his
OL,5,Cbirthday
OL,7,FJames Van Der Beek's nine-year-old
OL,8,Fdaughter has paid tribute to her late
OL,9,Ffather almost one month after he died
OL,10,Fof bowel cancer.
OL,12,FOn what would have been Dawson Creek's
OL,13,Factor's 49th birthday on Sunday,
OL,14,FEmilia opened up about her struggles
OL,15,Fwith grief.
OL,17,F"So today is my dad's birthday. And
OL,18,Fthe number one thing for somebody's
OL,19,Fpassing is to talk to them and let
OL,20,Fyour emotions out," she said in an
OL,21,FInstagram video.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
