PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1773079567
OL,3,CJames Van Der Beek's daughter, 9,
OL,4,Cposts tribute to late father on his
OL,5,Cbirthday
OL,7,F"If you miss them, you can cry, you
OL,8,Fcan talk to them. I talk to my dad
OL,9,Fevery day... I say, 'Hi dad, I miss
OL,10,Fyou and I love you so much and I'll
OL,11,Fnever stop loving you.' And I just
OL,12,Ftell him about my day, how I'm feeling
OL,13,Fand I tell my family how I'm feeling,
OL,14,Fand I know he can hear me, but I can't
OL,15,Fhear him."
OL,17,FShe continued: "I know that my dad's
OL,18,Fin a good place. He's not in pain
OL,19,Fanymore. He's in heaven.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1773079567
OL,3,CJames Van Der Beek's daughter, 9,
OL,4,Cposts tribute to late father on his
OL,5,Cbirthday
OL,7,F"Be happy they're in a good place. Be
OL,8,Fsad because you miss them. You can be
OL,9,Fangry, but don't blame yourself.
OL,10,FBlaming yourself, it's not a good
OL,11,Fstrategy for someone's passing."
OL,13,FVan Der Beek died in February, aged
OL,14,F48, after he revealed in 2024 that he
OL,15,Fwas being treated for bowel cancer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
