OL,3,CJames Van Der Beek's daughter, 9,
OL,4,Cposts tribute to late father on his
OL,5,Cbirthday
OL,7,FThe actor was best known for playing
OL,8,Fthe titular character in the US teen
OL,9,Fdrama Dawson's Creek, which ran for
OL,10,Fsix seasons from 1998 until 2003, and
OL,11,Ffollowed a group of friends navigating
OL,12,Fadolescence.
OL,14,FHe is survived by his wife, Kimberly,
OL,15,Fand their six children: Olivia, 15;
OL,16,FJoshua, 13; Annabel, 12; Emilia, 9;
OL,17,FGwendolyn, 7; and Jeremiah, 4.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
